data.description: Get ready to call this house your next home or investment property! This home is ready for a buyer to put their personal touch on the home. Upstairs boasts a large eat-in kitchen, dining room, family room, 2 secondary bedrooms, full bath, and the primary suite. Downstairs has 2 additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a laundry room. The 2-car garage has an oversized storage closet. Located on a corner lot in a community with no rental restrictions.
